ng-submit.
    - used to submit the form at a time to the controller.

Syntax.
<form ng-submit="login_details()">

    //Form Elements

    <input type="submit"></input>
</form>

ng-switch.
    - used write the switch cases in Angular Applications.

Syntax.
<div ng-switch="expression">
    <div ng-switch-when="value_one">
            --
            --
    </div>
    <div ng-switch-when="value_two">
                --
                --
    </div>
    <div ng-switch-when="value_three">
                --
                --
    </div>
    <div ng-switch-default>
                --
                --
    </div>
</div>



ng-cloak.

    - used to eliminate the flickering / blinking

      of web page before displaying result.


Syntax.

<div ng-cloak>

</div>


Mouse Events.

    - when ever we perform the mouse events ,

      automatically coresponding directives will be executed by Angular Framework.


 Syntax.

    ng-mousedown /
    ng-mouseup/
                        "user defined function"
    ng-mouseenter/
    ng-mouseleave/